tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE GenderBasedViolenceIncidents (
  incident_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  incident_date DATE,
  location VARCHAR,
  description TEXT,
  support_service_id INT REFERENCES SupportServices(service_id)
)

CREATE TABLE incidents (
  incident_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  incident_date DATE,
  description TEXT,
  location VARCHAR(255),
  status VARCHAR(50)
);

CREATE TABLE support_services (
  service_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  service_name VARCHAR(255),
  description TEXT,
  contact_number VARCHAR(15),
  contact_email VARCHAR(50)
);

CREATE TABLE Incident (
  incident_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  incident_date DATE,
  incident_description TEXT,
  location VARCHAR(255),
  reported_by VARCHAR(100)
)

CREATE TABLE SupportService (
  service_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  service_name VARCHAR(100),
  service_type VARCHAR(50),
  contact_email VARCHAR(100),
  contact_phone VARCHAR(15)
)

CREATE TABLE ServiceFeedback (
  feedback_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  service_id INT,
  rating INT,
  comment TEXT,
  feedback_date DATE,
  FOREIGN KEY (service_id) REFERENCES SupportService(service_id)
)

CREATE TABLE support_services (
   id INT PRIMARY KEY,
   service_name VARCHAR(100),
   service_type VARCHAR(50),
   location VARCHAR(100),
   contact_number VARCHAR(20)
);

CREATE TABLE victims (
   id INT PRIMARY KEY,
   victim_name VARCHAR(100),
   age INT,
   gender VARCHAR(10),
   incident_id INT
);

CREATE TABLE reports (
   id INT PRIMARY KEY,
   report_date DATE,
   report_description TEXT,
   victim_id INT,
   support_service_id INT
);
